description:
.1-.4 - outline of tree
.5 - silhouette of tree [WPI] and [MK] at bottom in pencil
.6 - silhouette of top of tree with shaded trunk;[WP2] and [MK] at bottom in pencil
.7 - lightly shaded tree; [WP3] and [MK] at bottom in pencil
.8 - shaded tree; [WP4] and [MK] at bottom in pencil
.9 - shaded tree; [WP5] and [MK] at bottom in pencil
.10 - lightly shaded tree 
.11 - dark tree with light tips on leaves
.12 - tree and background all over lighter than .11
.13 - tree and foreground all with cross-hatch type marks
.4 - tree very lightly shaded
.15 - tree very light - Maker: Michael Karaken; etching and aquatint; [WP6] and [MK] at bottom of print
.16 - tree with dark lines; Maker: Fred Hagstrom; engraving
.17 - tree with dark lines
[all prints have word \'intaglio\' at bottom]
[.13 - .17 are matted]
title: 17 examples of intaglio prints
